This torrent should be praised because this movie is rarely found elsewhere. 
However in all fairness, it may be said that the quality of the movie is very bad. It is made obvious from the first frame itself, when the title and cast starts. The cast is seen cut off from both sides. You can only read half names. This shows that the movie was probably shot by someone with a shoddy camera within a cinema hall.
